Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.43,0:01:23.76,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果てしない空をゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.86,0:01:27.15,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見えない翼が導く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.26,0:01:29.17,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥か彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.27,0:01:35.91,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}僕らを待つ　まだ見ぬ未来へと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.51,0:01:45.57,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Always　覚め切ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.74,0:01:48.57,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速すぎるthat night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.77,0:01:55.31,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透明な闇に囲まれ　誰も似た輪の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.41,0:01:58.38,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Find you　あの日の風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.50,0:02:01.71,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揺れ動いた場所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.79,0:02:03.04,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eternal my pass
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.09,0:02:07.99,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全て君に合うためのプロセスだったね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.38,0:02:11.08,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slowly opened my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.14,0:02:13.51,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We need the brightness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.99,0:02:17.45,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方から聞こえる予感に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.50,0:02:21.55,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓動を震わせていたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.97,0:02:25.34,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a reality　It's a reality
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.40,0:02:28.82,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you can believe myself for again
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.93,0:02:32.22,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光の中 目覚めていく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.27,0:02:35.88,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信じてくれた君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.94,0:02:37.08,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never let it go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:38.32,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never lost my way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.36,0:02:41.70,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ここで生まれ変わる景色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.83,0:02:45.28,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷さえ今　誇りになる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.32,0:02:49.89,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}だから君とBurst The Gravity
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.94,0:00:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.43,0:01:23.76,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在没有尽头的天空中行走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.86,0:01:27.15,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由看不见的羽翼引导
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.26,0:01:29.17,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通向遥远的比方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.27,0:01:35.91,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}那看不见的未来依旧在等待我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.51,0:01:45.57,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Always 不愿清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.74,0:01:48.57,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太快了 that night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.77,0:01:55.31,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被那透明的黑暗包围 谁也逃不出这个圈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.41,0:01:58.38,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Find you 那日的风
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.50,0:02:01.71,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变幻不定的场所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.79,0:02:03.04,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eternal my pass
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.09,0:02:07.99,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切都是为了与你相会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.38,0:02:11.08,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slowly opened my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.14,0:02:13.51,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We need the brightness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.99,0:02:17.45,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自彼方听闻的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.50,0:02:21.55,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令我震动鼓舞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.97,0:02:25.34,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a reality　It's a reality
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.40,0:02:28.82,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you can believe myself for again
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.93,0:02:32.22,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在光的沐浴下 我渐渐清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.27,0:02:35.88,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是你 我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.94,0:02:37.08,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never let it go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:38.32,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never lost my way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.36,0:02:41.70,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里不断变化的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.83,0:02:45.28,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的伤口 是我的骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.32,0:02:49.89,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}因为你和Burst The Gravity
