Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.50,0:00:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.53,0:00:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有出现在搜索列表上的超频连接者的名字是叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.53,0:00:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(492,430)}<Burst Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.64,0:00:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终线锯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.64,0:00:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Rust Jigsaw>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.77,0:00:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.33,0:00:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来坐在这边小兄弟有点头绪的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 其实我平时连接的局域网里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有个会这种把戏的其他连接者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(576,430)}<Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.99,0:00:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么 那家伙也会用这种手段
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.19,0:00:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛程安排人 你说的最终线锯等级跟类型是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.19,0:00:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(443,430)}<Rust Jigsaw>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.40,0:00:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等级是6 跟你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.43,0:00:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颜色也是名符其实的Rust
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.72,0:00:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是铁锈色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.65,0:00:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙擅长保持中远距离应战 专门猎杀近战型的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.66,0:00:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说以近战为主的你 打起来会很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.16,0:00:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K 那么就将计就计好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.70,0:00:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就当作给你的情报费
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.94,0:00:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟他登记成双人组选手作为诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:00:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.85,0:01:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…如果说是你的名号的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.25,0:01:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为诱饵的确是很有诱惑力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.45,0:01:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这个新人没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.18,0:01:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说他到底是哪里的谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.06,0:01:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好比我更有名
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是复活了的黑暗星云军团旗下的白银之鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(396,430)}<Nega Nebulas>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.49,0:02:56.45,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\pos(663,400)}Determination；决意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.62,0:02:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H8DFCFD&\an5\fs18\frz8\3c&H1919BC&\8frx\pos(389,322)}有人来挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.37,0:02:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 日珥的「豹」要下场耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.37,0:02:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs18\pos(317,430)}<Prominence>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.89,0:03:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么她会和黑暗星云军团旗下的「鸦」联手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.14,0:03:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是组队 单独行动的最终线锯会来么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.13,0:03:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(525,430)}<Rust Jigsaw>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.19,0:03:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你似乎飞不起来的传闻也已经传得很开了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.90,0:03:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要他知道了 袭击我们的可能性非常高
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.86,0:03:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把我秒杀了 接下来就可以和你一对一挑战了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.94,0:03:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有我想到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.63,0:03:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要连接局域网的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.37,0:03:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jigsaw的真身肯定会在这栋楼里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.72,0:03:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们有没有办法找到他真人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.60,0:03:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许有方法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.53,0:03:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么方法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.57,0:03:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚点我再和你解释
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.86,0:03:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非敌人先用 否则千万不能动用心念系统
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.84,0:03:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个红之王也吩咐过了 但为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.24,0:03:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.36,0:03:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心意是自己心灵里的洞的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.59,0:04:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每从里面抽取力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都会渐渐被拉进那个黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.46,0:04:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.54,0:04:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾与之战斗过的「灾祸之铠」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.73,0:04:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制造出那个东西的就是初代灾星失控的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.74,0:04:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(520,430)}<Disaster>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以王们都在遏制心意的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.13,0:04:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像Brain Burst一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心念系统也是一体两面的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.72,0:04:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望的另一面是绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此 我还是想要相信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.07,0:04:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信心意…相信愿望的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.83,0:04:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…应该说想相信曾经拯救我的Brain Burst
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.87,0:04:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 Rain说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.07,0:04:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…也许能改变这个加速世…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.67,0:04:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.83,0:05:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K 上钩了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.13,0:05:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jigsaw估计首先会用远距离攻击将我们分开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.64,0:05:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从你开始下手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.91,0:05:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不要和我离开太远
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.39,0:05:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚应该就是这家伙的远程攻击轮锯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.31,0:05:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全看不见轮锯本体
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.92,0:05:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能听声反应了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.73,0:05:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲过下次攻击后就一口气缩短距离
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.80,0:05:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要犹豫 飞起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.21,0:05:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终线锯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.21,0:05:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Rust Jigsaw>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.47,0:06:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会放你跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.75,0:06:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.28,0:06:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好你是金属系的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.29,0:06:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 刚才的那是那家伙的另一招
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定位锯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Still Saw>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.96,0:06:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一种将线锯固定在空中的招式
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个阻挡对手 再用轮锯持续进行远程攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是近战型的天敌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.81,0:06:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必杀技计量表借给我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.67,0:06:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变形
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐上来 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮锯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Wheel Saw>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.91,0:07:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.33,0:07:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.17,0:07:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然快 但还是比不上子弹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.42,0:07:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GJ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.91,0:07:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.23,0:07:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good Game
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.64,0:08:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起来 要出店了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.51,0:08:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的话或许可以特定他的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终线锯的真实身份
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.01,0:08:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(355,430)}<Rust Jigsaw>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.56,0:08:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才在Jigsawi的左肩上给予了连续打击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.62,0:08:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那么深刻的痛觉感受
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算回到了现实短时间内还是有影响的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.71,0:08:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在入口附近 找找看有没有那种神态的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.74,0:08:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那家伙吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.38,0:08:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请收下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.69,0:08:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Crow
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.60,0:08:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.12,0:08:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是我一个人在艰苦修行的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.21,0:08:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又在和年长的美女约会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.83,0:08:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说不是约会啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.47,0:09:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是在对战圣地约会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.98,0:09:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是要修行 我也想去看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这么说的话 你不也一直在跟仁子对战？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.41,0:09:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不巧的是她只在最开始和最后阶段指导了我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.71,0:09:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后听说难得有狩猎Enemy的机会就跑没影了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.94,0:09:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 心意系统的修行还顺利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.09,0:09:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「还远远不到能在实战中使用的程度」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.78,0:09:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用红之王的话来说就是这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.51,0:09:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我还是觉得我抓住了些小窍门
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 太好了 小拓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.37,0:09:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春也是 不管结果怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是做得很好 辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就是等秋叶原BG提供情报了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈祷那人能通过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.83,0:09:41.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春告诉他那家伙现实世界的特征
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到Jigsaw的现实身份吧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.01,0:09:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是 谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.74,0:09:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就明天学校见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.59,0:09:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 事情不会这么简单啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.40,0:09:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我哦 小千
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.35,0:10:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之我会想办法 把你从那混蛋的威胁中解放出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.55,0:10:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这就当做我们的出道战好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青橙铃音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Lime Bell>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.15,0:10:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.41,0:10:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚 小千好像和能美联手在新宿跟人对战了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百分之百的胜率？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是从新宿地区的熟人那里听说的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.72,0:10:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说 如果等黄昏掠夺者必杀技槽集满
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.71,0:10:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(413,430)}<Dusk Taker>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始飞行的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何对战虚拟角色都遇到他束手无策了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(355,430)}<Duel Avatar>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.29,0:10:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会演变成那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:10:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有治愈师充当后盾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:10:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远距离飞行型的对战角色
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙完全可以避开同等级 同潜力原则的限制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.63,0:11:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能美…可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 或许事态会比我们想象的还要严重
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.56,0:11:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春 我们应该有在心里这样想过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.59,0:11:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算能美再怎么强
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.60,0:11:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要Master 黑之睡莲回来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.58,0:11:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(441,430)}<Black Lotus>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就可以一刀两断 干脆地解决掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.82,0:11:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.45,0:11:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小拓 难道你是说会输吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐会输给能美吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.33,0:11:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想思考这种事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.77,0:11:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 事到如今必须想好最糟糕的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.61,0:11:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我们在周六之前也得做点力所能及的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.19,0:11:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 小春
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力所能及的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:12:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 只要不探明他如何在对战表上隐身的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.62,0:12:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的行动只会束手束脚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.11,0:12:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pard她们和秋叶原的人都还没查到什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.87,0:12:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来找你谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.26,0:12:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.14,0:12:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要谈什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.42,0:12:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在没去社团活动了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.43,0:12:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.58,0:12:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是能美的指示吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.54,0:13:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的话又怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.93,0:13:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把Brain Burst优先于现实世界是错误的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.61,0:13:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种话居然会从小春嘴里说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.34,0:13:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又没有参加社团
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.58,0:13:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有因为Brain Burst而忘记做作业
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.44,0:13:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 小春把这些以外的时间全部…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.70,0:13:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样啦 别那么认真啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是个游戏而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.89,0:13:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天就上升了两个等级哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.85,0:13:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有观众说我可能是Brain Burst史上最快的升级速度哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.33,0:13:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.26,0:13:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军团的邀请也多得我都不知道数量了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.26,0:13:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(231,430)}<Legion>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.47,0:13:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉突然就变成超受欢迎的人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.14,0:13:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再这样了 这完全不是你的作风啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.56,0:13:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会听能美的话是因为那段影像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错的是踩进陷阱的我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.46,0:13:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让能美为所欲为 被抓住弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果连你都被他夺走的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我要怎么办才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不明白啊 小春
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.94,0:14:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你完全不了解我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我在加速世界的对战角色对能美唯命是从
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.63,0:14:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(480,430)}<Avatar>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现实世界的我 在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.57,0:14:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在小春触手可及的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样 你还不明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.23,0:14:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有被夺走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是按照我的意志而行动的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.31,0:14:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前是这样 以后也是！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.39,0:14:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的意志…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.27,0:14:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白 小千到底在想什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.98,0:14:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.29,0:14:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 你把衣服穿好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.91,0:15:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.91,0:15:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以也请你相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.07,0:15:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不会输给能美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.94,0:15:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被夺走的东西 我也一定会夺回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.75,0:15:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.07,0:15:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 我也还有力所能及的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.66,0:15:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想 要好好思考 有田春雪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.43,0:15:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把所有的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.23,0:15:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从能美出现的所说的一字一句
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.54,0:15:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他的出现每一个地点 做的每一个动作都想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.51,0:15:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并加以推测
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.94,0:15:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是留给你的 最后的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这些 能美是夺不走的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.13,0:15:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定在哪里会有线索
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.01,0:15:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要把那家伙的秘密和弱点找出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:15:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能美的秘密…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.65,0:16:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 如果能控制最终线锯的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.65,0:16:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(497,430)}<Rust Jigsaw>
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.79,0:16:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个动作是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.11,0:16:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来以为他是在驱赶别人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.52,0:16:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.73,0:16:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且好像是看习惯了的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.44,0:16:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.45,0:16:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在关闭假想窗口
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.68,0:16:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他没有戴神经连结装置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.14,0:16:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是其他的电子装置吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.91,0:16:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 除了神经连结装置之外应该没有了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拍的很好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是神经连结装置以前的电子装置的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.00,0:16:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最早的VR机器
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.78,0:16:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是2020年代的NERvGear
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 那个只是完全潜行专用的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.33,0:16:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到拓展现实机能的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神经连结装置才是第一款
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.51,0:16:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.70,0:16:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这两者之间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.09,0:16:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像还有一个能拓展现实机能的电子装置
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.19,0:17:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大脑植入芯片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.19,0:17:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Brain Implant Chip>
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.18,0:17:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.33,0:17:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能美 这次我要和你做个了结
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游戏结束了 能美征二
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.11,0:17:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 黄昏掠夺者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.12,0:17:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(444,430)}<Dusk Taker>
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.86,0:17:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.36,0:17:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说 这次你要彻彻底底地认输了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.43,0:17:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你说「我投降了 不要在欺负我了」的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.84,0:17:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你错了 我只是说你我之间的游戏已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.53,0:17:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长 你还真是不识时务啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.91,0:17:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和黛学长已经什么都做不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.43,0:18:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会打败黑之王 统治这个学园
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.45,0:18:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…你只要老实地看着我统治衫并地区就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.88,0:18:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不会让你如愿的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.23,0:18:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不在对战搜索列表中出现的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.01,0:18:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为你脑中有两个VR装置
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.74,0:18:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,违法的大脑植入芯片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.74,0:18:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(465,431)}<Brain Implant Chip>
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.79,0:18:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大脑植入芯片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.79,0:18:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Brain Implant Chip>
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.45,0:18:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是植入在大脑皮层和三重脑髓黏膜的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.57,0:18:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最外层黏膜里的小型集成芯片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会有被发现的危险
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.73,0:18:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经常被用在考试时候作弊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.75,0:18:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以仅仅三年 就被严禁生产的违法电子装置
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.36,0:18:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你平时就是用大脑植入芯片连接校内网络
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.88,0:18:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并用这个上课和参加考试
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.54,0:18:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有在对战的瞬间才连接上神经连结装置
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.52,0:18:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(590,430)}<Neural Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.84,0:18:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你不出现在对战搜索列表中的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.16,0:18:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你植入那个东西的事曝光的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.06,0:18:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就会被勒令退学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.12,0:19:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芯片也会被处理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.83,0:19:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经完了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.98,0:19:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原以为你是猪 原来你是老鼠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.87,0:19:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是四处乱窜 让我心烦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.21,0:19:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从一开始你就应该先灭了我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.20,0:19:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有如此做 是你的失误
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.62,0:19:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我承认
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.36,0:19:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你想怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.99,0:19:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的「偷窥录像」和我的「植入违法芯片」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.82,0:19:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道要双方互不相让
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.11,0:19:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在现实世界中拼个两败俱伤么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.24,0:19:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了吗 能美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.28,0:19:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是超频连接者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.28,0:19:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(466,430)}<Burst Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.19,0:19:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超频连接者有自己的解决方式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.20,0:19:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(314,430)}<Burst Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.14,0:19:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想说 要对战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.07,0:19:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是讨厌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.90,0:19:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是超频连接者这个称呼 还是你的态度
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.90,0:19:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(323,430)}<Burst Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.57,0:19:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都十分厌恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.64,0:19:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但既然是学长你的希望 那我也没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.58,0:20:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我也有个提案 行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提案？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.14,0:20:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正学长是想双方战斗至点数全部失去为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.73,0:20:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正要打 不如就一战定胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.08,0:20:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用学长喜欢的决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在无限制中立舞台 把对战者的点数全部押上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.22,0:20:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢的一方就能获得所有的点数和道具
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.77,0:20:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用这个一决胜负如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.19,0:20:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 事情已经发展成这样了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.59,0:20:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 现在我发过去的是之后的交涉内容
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.54,0:20:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能美列出的条件列表
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.85,0:20:40.85,Warning,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs18\pos(511,157)\c&HEBEFEB&\3c&H2E2F2D&}决斗条件
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.85,0:20:40.85,Warning,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs15\c&HEBEFEB&\3c&H2E2F2D&\pos(402,272)}· 决斗在无限制中立舞台进行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.85,0:20:40.85,Warning,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs15\c&HEBEFEB&\3c&H2E2F2D&\pos(467,288)}· 决斗方法是双方押上自己所有的超频点数一决胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.85,0:20:40.85,Warning,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs18\c&HEBEFEB&\3c&H2E2F2D&\pos(499,314)}决斗保证
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.85,0:20:40.85,Warning,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs15\c&HEBEFEB&\3c&H2E2F2D&\pos(656,399)}· 允许【小拓的虚拟角色名 犯懒了】同行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.85,0:20:40.85,Warning,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs15\c&HEBEFEB&\3c&H2E2F2D&\pos(654,416)}· 决斗时间决定之前可以随意更改或延迟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.57,0:20:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么看 小拓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.53,0:20:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是接受这个申请的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.27,0:20:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是觉得太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在无限制中立舞台的话 就有伏兵的危险
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.89,0:20:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括允许我一同前往在内…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.23,0:21:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能美 一定还有什么胜算
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.05,0:21:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 胜算有多大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.59,0:21:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以随意更改对战场所
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.87,0:21:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就现实而言 伏击是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.39,0:21:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实 能想到的 只有花大量的超频点数
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.13,0:21:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是长时间潜伏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.81,0:21:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好 可能需要几个月的忍耐力的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.49,0:21:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个能美 有愿意如此为他卖命的朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有那样的朋友在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.04,0:21:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能美…就应该是个更加像样的超频连接者才对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.02,0:21:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(575,430)}<Burst Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.56,0:21:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 作为超频连接者的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.32,0:21:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和利用加速的能美之间的对决
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.19,0:21:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们借以立足的矜持 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.40,0:21:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 接受决斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.02,0:21:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小拓 在学姐回来之前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.88,0:21:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让一切结束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.84,0:22:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决战的时刻到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.98,0:23:40.99,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(687,392)}Consolidation ; 羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.44,0:23:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}下集 Consolidation
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.56,0:23:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}切开绝望的黑色光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.90,0:23:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}那是深刻羁绊的证明
